Reset one or more keys to defaults

Usage:
  grainfs cluster config reset <key> [<key> ...] [flags]

Flags:
  -h, --help                help for reset
      --if-match-rev uint   optimistic-concurrency: require this rev or fail with 409

Global Flags:
      --endpoint string    admin Unix socket path (required, e.g. ./tmp/admin.sock)
      --format string      Output format: text or json (status/peers/events; ignored elsewhere) (default "text")
      --log-level string   log level: debug, info, warn, error (default "info")
